Package: KMeans
Type: Package
Title: Apply K-Means Clustering Algorithm
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Shadmaan Hye
Maintainer: Shadmaan Hye <sh2742@nau.edu>
Description: The package provides a function named KMeans which takes a data of size (n x d), where n is the number of observations and d is dimension of the data.
    The return of the function is a class where "cluster" gives the K cluster centers of shape (K x d). And "tot.withinss" gives the sum of squared error of all the data from the clusters (which should be as low as possible for good clusters.
Imports: data.table
